<h1>Plug Into the {{community_name}} Community</h1>

<div class="registration_information">
  <ul class="infolist">
    <li>CommonPlace {{community_name}} is the best way to connect with the {{community_name}} community.</li>
    <li>Register a community profile and start sharing short updates with your neighborhood, the police chief, the mayor, and great local businesses in town.</li>
    <li>Since January 2011, 543 of your neighbors and 23 {{community_name}} organizations have shared 234 updates with the community.  Don't miss anything!</li>
  </ul>
  <ul class="link_item">
    <a href="{{learn_more}}">Learn more</a>
  </ul>
</div>

<form class="new_user">
  <h4>
    <a href="{{facebook}}"></a>
    Register Now
  </h4>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <input type="text" name="full_name" placeholder="Full name">
      <span class="error full_name"></span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email address">
      <span class="error email"></span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <input type="text" name="street_address" class="has_hint" placeholder="Street address">
      <div class="error address"></div>
      <span class="hint" style="display: none;">* This verifies you live in {{community_name}}. We will not share it with anyone.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
  
  <input type="image" src="/assets/buttons/signup2.png" class="sign_up">
</form>

<div style="clear: both;"></div>
